            <p><br />Notes:</p>
            
            <p>* Admissions staff at LEAPS partner Universities pledge to make offers to LEAPS eligible applicants if at all possible. Students should be asked to meet the usual minimum offer, even if this means setting tough conditions. Please bear in mind that the LEAPS Summer School affords students with conditional offers an additional opportunity to demonstrate their potential to succeed on their chosen degree course should they fail to meet these conditions.</p>

            <p>** This could include academic and non-academic conditions e.g. portfolio, relevant experience, audition, interview. 
